<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">This is a list of notable political theorists. See the <a href="/wiki/List_of_political_scientists" title="List of political scientists">list of political scientists</a> for those who study <a href="/wiki/Politics" title="Politics">politics</a> using the <a href="/wiki/Scientific_method" title="Scientific method">scientific method</a>.</div>
